Marriott is my preferred chain and never disappoints... except this time.	I've been at all three of the Key West Marriott Hotels and this is my favorite for value and relaxation.	The hotel also has a list of restaurant recommendations, which are staff favorites.	I totally recommend this hotel when you are in Key West either for business or pleasure!	I will continue to book other hotels in the Marriott chain however not this location.	We are very loyal Marriott customers and timeshare owners and this is not the kind of service that we are used to from Marriott.	I work for a different hotel chain and have pretty high standards!	hotel prices are high in Key West in general.